comments: Beal (WAS) cleanly steals the ball from Jokic (DEN).
Murray (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Portis (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Bryant (WAS) as he establishes position in the post.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brown Jr. (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bryant (WAS) makes marginal contact to the body of Murray (DEN) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harris (DEN) and he avoids making contact.
Bryant (WAS) and Jokic (DEN) make incidental contact with each other going for the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Satoransky (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Satoransky (WAS) makes marginal contact with Murray (DEN) that does not affect his SQBR.
Barton (DEN) makes contact to the arm of Satoransky (WAS) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Harris (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bryant (WAS) and collapses his arms.  He does not deliver the contact.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brown Jr. (WAS) and does not deliver the contact.
Brown Jr. (WAS) makes marginal contact to the body of Murray (DEN) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) dislodges Bryant (WAS) from his position during the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brown Jr. (WAS) and does not deliver contact.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Beal (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bryant (WAS) makes contact to the arm of Harris (DEN) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
LAR shows Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Beal's (WAS) arm that does not affect his ability to secure the pass that hits his leg.
Bryant (WAS) firms up his screening position in the path of Murray (DEN) and does not deliver contact.
Satoransky (WAS) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
Bryant (WAS) commits a take foul on Harris (DEN).
Bryant (WAS) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage and separate during the rebound.
Beal (WAS) commits a take foul on Harris (DEN).
Craig (DEN) makes contact with the ball and incidental contact with Satoransky's (WAS) arm during the loose ball.
Bryant (WAS) makes contact with the ball and incidental contact with Plumlee's (DEN) body as he goes for the rebound.
